author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Black Diet, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2015.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Fever
00:03:47 State Line
00:06:46 Find a New Love

Musicians
Jonathan Tolliver — lead vocals
Mugsy — backing vocals
Mitch Sigurdson — guitar
Sean Schultz — keys, guitar
Garrison Grouse — bass
David Tullis — drums

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – David Campbell
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.

author: The Current
description:
Watch Samia and her band perform "Lizard" in studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Singer-songwriter Samia releases her second full-length album, 'Bloodless,' on April 25, 2025. Just a few weeks before the release, Samia visited The Current studio with some of her musical collaborators to perform four songs off the new album. Watch and listen to a performance of "Lizard" above.

Musicians
Samia Finnerty – vocals
Sam Rosenstone – keyboards, vocals
Jake Luppen – electric guitar, vocals
Nathan Stocker – six- and 12-string guitar, vocals

Credits

Producer – Derrick Stevens
